{"tid":2500388,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"運輸署都不敢答的問題 何以咬定記者「虛假陳述」？","createTime":"2021-04-22T14:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T15:45:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc84a34776960d68fec48d4a375ab5b7161be121","tid":2500388,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4QD9EO8pxZXricq6Y74jTt3td7c=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/75MDGPX24VFFZDV2CKNFGZRE4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4QD9EO8pxZXricq6Y74jTt3td7c%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F75MDGPX24VFFZDV2CKNFGZRE4Q.jpg&h=f57e3b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台編導蔡玉玲（阿包）的案件落幕，裁判官徐綺薇頒下26頁判詞，指小心考慮所有證供後，認為「唯一合理而不可抗拒」的推論是阿包「明知而作出在要項上的虛假陳述」，認為控方在「毫無合理疑點之下」證明兩項控罪中的所有犯罪元素，判她罪名成立，寫來字字鏗鏘。<br />\n<br />\n案件的核心在於運輸署提供予公眾申請查冊的網上表格，只得「進行法律程序」、「買賣車輛」、及「其他交通及運輸的事宜」三項聲明用途供選擇，阿包剔了她認為最接近的第三項，之後就被上門拘捕，告上法庭。<br />\n<br />\n法官指她為採訪及製作節目查冊，與「其他交通及運輸事宜」無關，所以她必然是作虛假陳述，更告誡「即使運輸署提供的三個選項均不適用，也不能夠作出虛假陳述」，也講得理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n記者必須再次分享去年申請查冊的經驗。阿包當時已經被捕，記者親身到運輸署辦事處，填實體表格，並向職員表明身份，問對方如果要為新聞報道而查冊，究竟應該如何填這份表格。<br />\n<br />\n職員聞言面有難色，到後面「問一問主任」後，回來竟然叫記者自行決定。記者追問，為交通相關新聞查冊，可否剔選「其他交通及運輸事宜」？職員回應：「係你自己揀返嘅，你覺得呢一個就呢一個，或者呢一個就呢一個囉。」再問下去，職員才暗示知悉阿包被捕的新聞，「所以我都唔敢答你呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/DIGFAXB4MFFZTDTH5ZFLPWYKZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FDIGFAXB4MFFZTDTH5ZFLPWYKZE%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrTsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=86c172c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210422%2FDIGFAXB4MFFZTDTH5ZFLPWYKZE%2F&h=1df7bdb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210422/DIGFAXB4MFFZTDTH5ZFLPWYKZE/</a>"},{"pid":"16bfab6be5eb9a3a6165a4de16b0fc2d76a31bbb","tid":2500388,"uid":126919,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"「所以我都唔敢答你呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd35adc45f2b3a7edb53beb9d55699d3fd6557f","tid":2500388,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5d0be895039b8e8503e54508e5fa904fdde546","tid":2500388,"uid":179718,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<br />\n人治法庭<br />\n調番轉藍絲起黃絲底<br />\n一來告都唔告<br />\n二來就算私人檢控又會介入，法官到時只會 wfc"},{"pid":"a393f2fcd8a34623e6aed9d473c8af2d21138055","tid":2500388,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"因為涉及國安問題 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"aee50a814987bf7eb0104460ec80c0e492debb75","tid":2500388,"uid":125279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"運吉署班友比人擺上枱姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed97992783a5ad1715d5f32947473abf29e7e077","tid":2500388,"uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"為左新聞/公眾利益點解唔計其他交通/運輸事宜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02bfe08dd1af94b3474d33f6eed19a801975499","tid":2500388,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=